---
import Modal from '../components/Modal.astro';
import Stats from './Stats.astro';
---

<Modal id="info" title="About DoctorPricer">
	<p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
		DoctorPricer was built to help New Zealanders find affordable healthcare. GP fees can vary drastically, so it uses pricing data from
		publicly available sources to help you make informed decisions.
	</p>
	<p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
		It is <strong>entirely independent, non-commercial, and DIY funded</strong>. If you'd like to help support, you can make a one-time or
		recurring donation here:
		<a href="https://ko-fi.com/doctorpricer" title="Donate at ko-fi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
			<img class="py-4 w-64" src="/kofi.png" />
		</a>
	</p>
	<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 m-0">Stats</h3>
	<Stats />
	<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 mt-4 italic">
		Disclaimer: Best efforts are made to keep data accurate, but practices can change their prices without warning. If pricing is wrong,
		please use the "Suggest an edit" button.
	</p>
	<div slot="footer" class="text-right">
		<button class="close-btn bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 text-gray-800 px-4 py-2 rounded font-medium transition-colors"> Got it </button>
	</div>
</Modal>
